        "**ðŸ¤– Feature** **Selection** **for** **Clustering**"

        "id": "UcoNzmfuTxsE"
      }

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "X = df[['Annual_Income', 'Spending_Score']]"

      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
        "X_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X)"

      "metadata": {
        "id": "CvcE10ey_5Di"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Elbow** **Method**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "rhqoleS3T5hD"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "wcss = []\n",
        "\n",
        "for i in range(1, 11):\n",
        "    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=i, random_state=42)\n",
        "    kmeans.fit(X_scaled)\n",
        "    wcss.append(kmeans.inertia_)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "luBGL5U1S3na"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))\n",
        "plt.plot(range(1,11), wcss, marker='o', color='red')\n",
        "plt.title(\"Elbow Method to Find Optimal Clusters\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Number of Clusters\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"WCSS\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
